<br>
The flower quest in Mistmoore is to get a flower off the coffin in the crypt in the graveyard. Give it to Ssynthi, the shadowed man behind the crypt.<br>
<br>
You gain SolusekRo faction from this quest, not beta neutral. Be prepared to do this quest a LOT to build faction.<br>
<br>
Another way to boost SR faction is to kill shadowed men.<br>
<br>
You can also turn in derv rings to Ortallius the orc in South Ro for faction.<br>
<br>
I was KOS to the NPCs in the temple and KOS to Ortallius. I spent 20 hours camping shadowed men, zoned into the temple and was promptly killed.<br>
<br>
The easiest and fastest way to build faction is through cold hard cash. I was KOS to Ortallius the orc, but I was not KOS to Rathmana, the NPC in the tent behind Ortallius. I invised myself and went to the far back corner of the tent, where it was safe to drop invis. I then proceeded to hand 30 gold to Rathmana repeatedly (I brought 3500 gold) until I was out. After that, my faction was amiable in the temple again.<br>
<br>
Rathmana is on Solusek Ro faction as well, but he is more tolerant of those who are KOS to others. Good thing since he's a level 50 wizard.<br>
<br>
Good luck to your friend! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugrindel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Grindel</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(11/7/00 8:51:38 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=70.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.creighton.edu/~chrisj/elminster.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Beta Neutral faction</span><hr size=1> Yah that's right.  As far as his beta neutral faction goes, he finally tracked down a GM who reset it.  Thanks for the help. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uqinadann.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Qinadann</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/1/00 1:25:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=70.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Beta Neutral faction</span><hr size=1> You can also get some betaneutral faction for doing the Tishan's kilt quest.  I recently finished this quest since all the items required for it got so much easier.  Exactly not the best item but still you get to wear a skirt that gives you str. =)  <br>
